. 有能力的,胜任的,足够的',' Is Mary competent as a teacher?<br>     玛丽胜任教师的工作吗？<br>\n We know you are competent in doing this job.<br>     我们知道你可以胜任这项工作。<br>'),(1653,'competition','','','','competitions','n. 比赛,竞争',' Everyone in modern society faces the keen competition.<br>     现代社会的每个人都面临着激烈的竞争。<br>\n The team were on excellent form throughout the whole competition.<br>     这个队在整个比赛过程中一直处於极好的竞技状态。<br>'),(1654,'competitive','','','','','a. 竞争的,比赛的',' America is a competitive society.<br>     美国是一个充满竞争的社会。<br>\n Our prices are competitive.<br>     我们的价格是有竞争性的。<br>'),(1655,'competitor','','','','competitors','n. 竞争者',' The firm has better products than its competitors.<br>     这家公司的产品比其对手的好。<br>\n That company is a strong competitor of us.<br>     那个公司是我们强有力的竞争对手。<br>'),(1656,'compilation','','','','','n. 编译,编辑',' Her latest album is a compilation of all her best singles.<br>     她最新的一套唱片是她的最佳单曲唱片的汇集.<br>'),(1657,'compile','compiled','compiled','compiling','','v. 编译,编辑,编纂<br>\n[计算机] 编译',' It take year of hard work to compile a good dictionary.<br>     编纂一部好词典要花多年心血。<br>\n It takes years of hard work to compile a good dictionary.<br>     编一部好词典需要多年的艰苦工作。<br>'),(1658,'compiler','','','','','编译器,编译程序',' Optimize32 bit native code compiler with up to300%-400% faster application.<br>     优化32位本机代码编译器使应用程序加快了300％－400％。<br>\n In data security, the transmission of data to unauthorized users by processes with legitimate access to data. A compiler, for example, could leak a proprietary program whilst it is being compiled.<br>     在数据保密学中，通过合法访问数据的进程将数据传输给未授权的用户的过程。例如，编译程序在编译期间便可能泄漏专用程序。<br>'),(1659,'complain','complained','complained','complaining','','v. 抱怨,悲叹,控诉',' They complained bitterly about the injustice of the system.<br>     他们愤恨地抱怨制度不公平。<br>\n The tourist complained that the room was too dirty.<br>     游客抱怨说房间太脏了。<br>'),(1660,'complaint','','','','complaints','n. 抱怨',' I have a complaint of the chest.<br>     我胸部不适。<br>\n You have no cause for complaint.<br>     你没有理由抱怨。<br>'),(1661,'complement','','','','','n. 补足物,补语,余角<br>\nv. 补助',' This wine complements the food perfectly.<br>     用这种酒配这种菜肴最妙不过了。<br>\n A wine is a complement to a good meal.<br>     美食加美酒才算完备。<br>'),(1662,'complete','completed','completed','completing','','a. 彻底的,完整的,已完成的<br>\nv. 完成,使完整',' I will complete this task soon.<br>     我很快就要完成这项任务了。<br>\n When will the work be complete?<br>     这项工作什么时候完成？<br>'),(1663,'completely','','','','','ad. 完全地,十分地,全然',' The army made a completely successful attack on the enemy capital.<br>     军队攻击敌人首都的行动非常成功。<br>\n She tried to understand the instructions, but she was completely at sea.<br>     她费尽力气想看懂那些说明文字，却全然不知所云。<br>'),(1664,'completion','','','','completions','n. 完成,完满',' Completion of the building work is taking longer than expected.<br>     建筑工程的竣工比预计时间要长。<br>\n The film is on the point of completion.<br>     电影制作即将完成。<br>'),(1665,'complex','','','','complexes','a. 复杂的<br>\nn. 复合体',' Life is getting more complex and difficult.<br>     生活正在变得越来越复杂和艰难。<br>\n He has a complex about his weight.<br>     他过分关心自己的体重。<br>'),(1666,'complexion','complexioned','complexioned','complexioning','complexions','n. 外观(状态,形势,开色,配容)<br>\nvt 染(上色)',' This great victory changed the complexion of the war.<br>     这次大捷使整个战局为之改观。<br>\n He has a dark complexion.<br>     他肤色黝黑。<br>'),(1667,'complexity','','','','complexities','n. 复杂(性),复杂的事物',' We are facing a problem of great complexity.<br>     我们正面对着一个极复杂的问题。<br>\n It is a complexity of higher mathematics.<br>     这是一道高等数学的难题。<br>'),(1668,'compliance','','','','','n. 承诺,顺从,遵从',' In compliance with your wishes (ie As you have requested) we have withdrawn our suggestion.<br>     遵照你的要求我们已将建议撤销.<br>\n Compliance (with the rules) is expected of all members.<br>     要求全体人员都遵守（制度）.<br>'),(1669,'complicate','complicated','complicated','complicating','','v. 弄复杂,使错综,使起纠纷',' Her refusal to help complicates matters.<br>     她不肯帮忙，事情就更难办了。<br>\n Don\'t complicate life for me!<br>     不要为我把生活搞复杂了！<br>'),(1670,'c