(1829,'contiguous','','','','','a. 邻近的,接近的',' California and Mexico are contiguous.<br>     加利福尼亚和墨西哥相邻。<br>\n In Series/1, a series of contiguous records in a volume that describe the contents in terms of allocated data sets and free space.<br>     在IBMSeries／1中，文卷里的一串连续记录，这些记录用于描述已分配数据集和自由空间。<br>'),(1830,'continent','','','','','n. 大陆,洲',' There are seven continents in the world.<br>     世界上有七大洲。<br>\n The Antarctica is a continent centered roughly on the South Pole.<br>     南极洲是一片大致以南极为中心的大陆。<br>'),(1831,'contingency','','','','contingencies','n. 偶然(列联,意外费用,相切)',' The classification of propositions on the basis of whether they assert or deny the possibility, impossibility, contingency, or necessity of their content.<br>     模态逻辑命题的限制条件，建立在其内容的肯定或否定其可能性，不可能性，偶然性或必然性基础之上<br>\n It\'s impossible to legislate for every contingency.<br>     为每一偶发事件都立法是不可能的.<br>'),(1832,'continual','','','','','a. 不断的,频繁的',' Are you tired of this continual rain?<br>     你对于这不停的雨不感到厌烦吗？<br>\n Please stop your continual questions.<br>     请不要再接二连三地提问了。<br>'),(1833,'continue','continued','continued','continuing','','v. 继续,连续',' The fighting around the airport continued for a week before the enemy was defeated.<br>     机场附近的战斗持续了一个星期，敌军才被击溃。<br>\n Wet weather may continue for a few more days.<br>     多雨的天气可能还要持续好几天.<br>'),(1834,'continued','','','','','a. 继续的, 延续的',' The state of being continued.<br>     被继续被继续的状态<br>\n Edison and his men were watching his light all the night. The light continued to burn for40 hours before it went out.<br>     爱迪生和他的同伴整晚上在观察他的灯，灯连续亮了40个小时才熄灭。<br>'),(1835,'continuity','','','','','n. 连续性',' We must ensure continuity of fuel supplies.<br>     我们应该确保燃料供给不中断.<br>\n Continuity is ensured by using the same props in successive scenes.<br>     在连续的场景中使用同样的道具以确保前後衔接.<br>'),(1836,'continuous','','','','','a. 连续的,继续的,连棉不断的',' The brain needs a continuous supply of blood.<br>     大脑需要不断地供血。<br>\n Continuous assessment is made of all students\' work.<br>     对全体学生的功课作出连