c.<br>     我有一套音乐百科全书。<br>'),(2971,'encyclopedia','','','','encyclopedias','n. 百科全书',' We bought a multimedia encyclopedia.<br>     我们买了一套多媒体百科全书。<br>\n This encyclopedia is truly a compendium of knowledge.<br>     这部百科全书真正是知识宝库.<br>'),(2972,'end','ended','ended','ending','ends','n. 结束,终点,目标<br>\nv. 结束,终结,终止',' At the end of the film, the hero wept bitterly.<br>     在影片的结尾，主人公伤心地哭了。<br>\n They ended the party off with a song.<br>     他们唱支歌结束了晚会。<br>'),(2973,'endanger','endangered','endangered','endangering','','v. 危及',' If we falter in our leadership, we may endanger the peace of the world, and we shall surely endanger the welfare of this nation.<br>     如果我们的领导地位动摇了，不仅会危害世界的和平，而且一定会危害国家的安定。<br>\n He took over the post in the knowledge that it might endanger his life.<br>     他在明知他的性命有可能受到威胁的情况下接任了那职位。<br>'),(2974,'endeavor','endeavored','endeavored','endeavoring','endeavors','n. 努力,尽力<br>\nv. 努力,尽力',' The man endeavored to please his beloved wife.<br>     那人尽量使他深爱的妻子快乐。<br>\n Please make every endeavor to be early.<br>     请尽量早点儿。<br>'),(2975,'endeavour','endeavoured','endeavoured','endeavouring','endeavours','n. 奋力号(航船的名字)',' I shall endeavour to accommodate you whenever possible.<br>     只要有可能, 我将尽力帮你.<br>\n On account of your health, you must endeavour to shift off the care of your children.<br>     由于你身体不好，你必须尽量避免为孩子们操心。<br>'),(2976,'ending','','','','endings','n. 结尾,结局',' The story has a happy ending.<br>     这个故事有一个美满的结局。<br>\n His ending was peaceful.<br>     他很安详地去世。<br>'),(2977,'endless','','','','','a. 无止境的,没完没了的',' Her endless patience made her the best nurse in the hospital.<br>     无限的耐心使她成为这个医院最好的护士。<br>\n His endless talking hinders me from my study.<br>     他没完没了的谈话妨碍了我的学习。<br>'),(2978,'endnote','','','','','尾注',''),(2979,'endocrine','','','','','a. 内分泌的<br>\nn. 内分泌',''),(2980,'endorse','endorsed','endorsed','endorsing','','v. 支持,赞同,背书于',' He\'s had his license endorsed for dangerous driving.<br>     他的驾驶执照上载有危险驾驶记录。<br>\n I am afraid I can\'t endor