s enjoyable as possible.<br>     旅馆工作人员对我们照顾得无微不至，尽量让我们住得舒适，<br>'),(3009,'enjoyment','','','','enjoyments','n. 享受',' I didn\'t get much enjoyment out of that novel.<br>     我并没有从那本小说里得到多少乐趣。<br>\n Enjoyment of vigorous health and physical drives.<br>     动物特性对强健的身体及活跃的身体机能的享受<br>'),(3010,'enlarge','enlarged','enlarged','enlarging','','v. 扩大,增大',' I needn\'t enlarge upon this matter; you all know my views.<br>     我不需要详述此事；你们都知道我的意见。<br>\n I planned to enlarge this photograph.<br>     我计划放大这张照片。<br>'),(3011,'enlargement','','','','enlargements','n. 扩大',' Enlargement of the heart.<br>     心肥大心脏的扩大<br>\n The enlargement brings out the details in the photograph.<br>     照片放大後细微之处都很清楚.<br>'),(3012,'enlighten','enlightened','enlightened','enlightening','','v. 授与...知识,启发,启蒙',' Can you enlighten me on this subject?<br>     关于这个问题，你能指点我一下吗？<br>\n She was anxious to enlighten me about the events that led up to the dispute.<br>     她急着要使我明白引起这场争执的那些事情。<br>'),(3013,'enlightening','','','','','a. 有启迪作用的,使人感悟的',' The act or a means of enlightening.<br>     启迪启迪的行为或方式<br>\n She was anxious to enlighten me about the events that led up to the dispute.<br>     她急着要使我明白引起这场争执的那些事情。<br>'),(3014,'enormous','','','','','a. 巨大的,庞大的',' Long ago enormous animals lived on the earth.<br>     很久以前，地球上生活着巨大的动物。<br>\n Of enormous size or magnitude; huge.<br>     巨大的，庞大的规模巨大或大得出奇的；巨大的<br>'),(3015,'enough','','','','','a. 足够的<br>\nad. 足够地<br>\nn. 充足,足够<br>\npron. 足够(的)',' Enough is as good as a feast.<br>     知足常乐。<br>\n I\'ve had enough of her continual chatter.<br>     我已厌烦了她喋喋不休的闲谈。<br>'),(3016,'enquire','enquired','enquired','enquiring','','=inquire<br>\nv. 询问,调查',' I must enquire further into this matter.<br>     我要进一步调查此事.<br>\n For sale: small motor scooter. Enquire within.<br>     待售：小型摩托车，请进内询问。<br>'),(3017,'enquiry','','','','enquiries','n. 询问',' With respect to your enquiry, I enclose an explanatory leaflet.<br>     关於你的询问, 兹附上有关说明资料.<br>\n I am sorry, I am not able to help you with you