een the social services and local doctors.<br>     社会公益服务机构和当地医生应该加强协作。<br>\n The dynamics of bodies moving relative to gases, especially the interaction of moving objects with the atmosphere.<br>     空气动力学相对于气体的物体移动，特别是移动物体与大气相互作用的动力学<br>'),(4920,'interactive','','','','','[计算机] 交互的',' Our English software is an interactive educational software.<br>     我们的英语软件是一种交互式教育软件。<br>\n But its truly revolutionary character can be seen in its interactive potential.<br>     但它真正革命的特性能够在其相互影响的潜力方面表现出来。<br>'),(4921,'intercept','','','','','n. 截取,妨碍,截距<br>\nv. 拦截,阻止,截取<br>\n[计算机] 截断',' Reporters intercepted him as he tried to leave by the rear entrance.<br>     他想从后门溜走，记者把他截住了。<br>\n The police had been intercepting my mails.<br>     警方一直截查我的邮件。<br>'),(4922,'intercepting','','','','','截取',' The police had been intercepting my mails.<br>     警方一直截查我的邮件。<br>\n Effective defence is a matter of intercepting their missiles before they can reach us.<br>     有效的防卫是不待对方导弹击中我们而先行将其拦截.<br>'),(4923,'interchange','','','','','n. 立体交叉道,互换<br>\nv. 交换,互换<br>\n[计算机] 互换',' We should leave the motorway at the next interchange.<br>     我们应该在下一个立体交叉道驶离高速公路。<br>\n The chief interchanged the diamond with some pieces of glass.<br>     那首领拿一些玻璃块替换了那些钻石。<br>'),(4924,'interconnect','interconnected','interconnected','interconnecting','','vt. 使互相连接',' It\'s strange how people\'s lives interconnect.<br>     人们的生活是如何互相联系在一起的, 真是不可思议.<br>\n A series of interconnected points.<br>     一系列相互连接的点。<br>'),(4925,'interconnections','','','','','n. 相互连接,彼此连系',''),(4926,'intercourse','','','','','n. 交往,交流,中断期间',' English is more widespread and more used in international intercourse than German.<br>     英语在国际交往中比德语使用得更为广泛。<br>\n A friendly intercourse has been opened between the two countries.<br>     两国已开始了亲密的往来。<br>'),(4927,'interest','interested','interested','interesting','interests','n. 兴趣,嗜好,利息<br>\nv. 使...感兴趣',' His two great interests in life are music and painting.<br>     音乐和绘画是他生活中的两大嗜好。<br>\n Politics has always interested me.<br>     我一直对政治学有兴趣。<br>'),(4928,'interested','','','','','a. 感兴趣的',' I tried to tell him about it, but he just wasn\'t interested.<br>     我想把这件事告诉他，可他简直不感兴趣。<br>\n Lots of times you have to pretend to join a parade in which you\'re not really interested in order to get where you\'re going.<br>     好多时候，为了要走到你想到的地点，你得假装成参加那一队你实在不感兴趣的行列走。<br>'),(4929,'interesting','','','','','a. 有趣的',' This book is interesting.<br>     这本书很有趣。<br>\n I think these interesting old customs should be preserved.<br>     我认为这些有趣的旧习俗应该保存下去。<br>'),(4930,'interface','','','','','n. 界面,接触面<br>\n[计算机] 界面,接口',' The firewall machine will require two ethernet card, one interface to the outside world and one to the master pop network.<br>     防火墙计算机要求2张以太网卡，一个对外部世界的接口和一个对主POP网络的接口。<br>\n Can you give me an explanation of the man-machine interface?<br>     你能给我解释一下人机接口吗？<br>'),(4931,'interfere','','','','','v. 妨碍,冲突,干涉',' I\'ll go tomorrow if nothing interferes.<br>     如果没有其他的事，我明天去。<br>\n Don\'t interfere with my business.<br>     不要干涉我的事情。<br>'),(4932,'interference','','','','interferences','n. 冲突,干涉<br>\n[计算机] 于涉',' I resented his interference in my affairs.<br>     我很不满他干预我的私事。<br>\n The television station apologized for the interference, which was due to bad weather conditions.<br>     电视台为出现的干扰表示歉意，那是由于恶劣的天气状况造成的。<br>'),(4933,'interferon','','','','','n. 干扰素',''),(4934,'interim','','','','','a. 中间的,暂时的,临时的<br>\nn. 中间时期,过渡时期,暂定',' The full report isn\'t ready yet, but you can see the interim report.<br>     正式报告尚未写好，但你可以先看看这份临时报告。<br>\n Acting or done ad interim; temporary.<br>     临时的暂时做事的；临时的<br>'),(4935,'interior','','','','interiors','a. 内部的,内地的,国内的,在内的<br>\nn. 内部',' The interior of the building is magnificent and luxurious<br>     大楼内部装饰得富丽堂皇。<br>\n Xi\'an is a city in the interior of China.<br>     西安是一个内陆城市。<br>'),(4936,'interlace','interlaced','interlaced','interlacing','','v. 使交织,使组合,使交错',' The interlacing branches on the picture look poetic.<br>     图上交错的树枝看起来很有