>'),(7777,'payable','','','','','a. 可付的,应付的,有利益的',' L/c is payable against your draft.<br>     信用证凭汇票付款。<br>\n The payment of the goods is payable in instalments.<br>     货款可以分期支付。<br>');
INSERT INTO `words` VALUES (7778,'paycheck','','','','','n. 工资',' \"I hope he went fishing and comes back tomorrow, but I wouldn\'t bet my paycheck on it, \" said state police superintendent Clinton Pagano….<br>     州警察局长帕加诺说，\"我希望他钓鱼去了，明天就回来。但是我可不愿意拿我的薪水打赌（并无十分把握）。\"……<br>\n The new appropriations bill could mean a larger paycheck for state employees.<br>     新的岁出预算案对国家雇员来说是一张更大的支票<br>'),(7779,'payday','','','','','n. 发薪日',' Every payday he gangs one on.<br>     没有哪个发薪日他不是喝得醉醺醺的。<br>\n I am broke now that it\'s just before payday.<br>     刚好在发薪日前我已一文不名。<br>'),(7780,'payee','','','','','n. 收款人,取款人',''),(7781,'payer','','','','','n. 支付者,付款人',' The government should have increased family allowances and clawed it back from rich tax payers.<br>     政府本来应该增加家庭津贴并向富有的纳税人收回这笔支出。<br>'),(7782,'payment','','','','payments','n. 支付,付款',' They demand prompt payment.<br>     他们要求立即付款。<br>\n The payment of the goods is payable in instalments.<br>     货款可以分期支付。<br>'),(7783,'payoff','','','','','n. 清算(成果,发工资,放线装置)<br>\na. 得出结果的',''),(7784,'payout','','','','','n. 花费,支出',' The company only exists on payouts from the government.<br>     这个公司仅靠政府救济补贴生存。<br>'),(7785,'payroll','','','','payrolls','n. 工资单(计算报告表)',' The firm\'s payroll has one field for gross pay and one for net pay.<br>     公司工资单上一部分是原工资，一部分是实发工资。<br>\n Lopped him from the payroll.<br>     将他从工资单上除名<br>'),(7786,'PC','','','','','(personal computer)个人计算机',' Maintenance of PC is in my element.<br>     我对电脑的维修保养很在行。<br>'),(7787,'PE','','','','','n. 体育',''),(7788,'pea','','','','peas','n. 豌豆',' The sisters are as alike as two peas.<br>     两姐妹长得一模一样。<br>\n This kind of pea has a long pod.<br>     这种豌豆长着长豆荚。<br>'),(7789,'peace','','','','','n. 和平',' Please let me do my work in peace.<br>     请让我安静地工作。<br>\n She\'s never at peace with herself.<br>     她总是静不下来.<br>'),(7790,'peaceable','','','','','a. 安静的,和平的',' I was pleased to see how peaceable the horse had become.<br>     我很高兴地看到这匹马变得这么温顺。<br>'),(7791,'peaceful','','','','','