cision.<br>     这个政治家做了一个幼稚的决定。<br>'),(8549,'politics','','','','','n. 政治',' What are your politics?<br>     你的政见是什么？<br>\n He is not interested in politics.<br>     他不喜欢政治。<br>'),(8550,'polity','','','','polities','n. 政府制度',' A male leader of an Islamic polity.<br>     哈里发伊斯兰教政治组织中的男性领导人<br>\n A member of a Protestant church not observing the doctrines, usage, or polity of a national or established church, especially the Church of England.<br>     不信奉国教的人新教教会的一个成员，他不遵从国家的或已建立的教会的教义、习惯做法或政体，尤指英国教会<br>'),(8551,'poll','','','','','n. 投票,民意测验,选举人民意<br>\nv. 轮询,获得...票,剪树枝',' A large vote was polled.<br>     投票踊跃。<br>\n The result of the poll won\'t be known until midnight.<br>     投票结果要到半夜才能知道。<br>'),(8552,'Pollard','','','','','帕洛德',' The willows need to be pollarded.<br>     这些柳树需截去树梢.<br>'),(8553,'pollen','pollened','pollened','pollening','','n. 花粉<br>\nv. 授粉给',' There is a high pollen count in the air.<br>     空气中有很高的花粉计数。<br>\n Anther is a part of a flower that contains the pollen.<br>     花药是花的雄蕊上带花粉的部分。<br>'),(8554,'pollinate','pollinated','pollinated','pollinating','','v. 给...授粉<br>\nvt. 授以花粉',''),(8555,'pollination','','','','','n. 授粉',''),(8556,'polling','','','','','n. 投票',' The result of the poll won\'t be known until midnight.<br>     投票结果要到半夜才能知道。<br>\n Of those poll, seven out of ten say they preferred brown bread.<br>     那些被调查者十人中有七人说他们比较爱吃黑面包。<br>'),(8557,'pollster','','','','','n. 民意测验专家,整理民意测验结果的人',' Even in closely contested elections, most of the pollsters have called the winners, often by margins close to vote tally. And the pollsters who missed were off by a hair.<br>     即使在胜负极为接近的选举当中，多数民意测验人员都测出了胜利者。胜负差距往往与点票结果接近。测验失误的人也所差微乎其微。<br>'),(8558,'pollutant','','','','','n. 污染物质',' Discharge pipe take pollutant away from the coastal area into the sea.<br>     排泄管道将污染性物质由沿海岸区排入大海。<br>'),(8559,'pollute','polluted','polluted','polluting','pollution 不可数名词','v. 弄脏,污染<br>\nvt. 污染',' The river has been polluted by waste products from the factory.<br>     这条河