ough to eat.<br>     他那时盘算的是如何填饱肚子.<br>'),(8880,'preoccupied','','','','','a. 心事重重的,出神的',' Deep in thought and heedless of present circumstances or activities; preoccupied.<br>     心不在焉的，茫然的陷入沉思且未注意到周围的情况或活动的；出神的<br>\n Health worries preoccupied him for the whole holiday.<br>     整个假期里他一直为健康状况而担忧.<br>'),(8881,'preoccupy','preoccupied','preoccupied','preoccupying','','v. 先占领,先取,迷住',' She seemed preoccupied all the time I was talking to her.<br>     我跟她讲话时她始终显得心事重重.<br>\n He answered me in a rather preoccupied manner.<br>     他心不在焉地回答我.<br>'),(8882,'preordain','preordained','preordained','preordaining','','v. 预定,预先注定',''),(8883,'prep','prepped','prepped','prepping','','n. (口语,preparatory的缩写形式)预备',' Prep a surface for painting.<br>     准备一个平面来作画<br>\n Four years of prep school should polish those children.<br>     四年的预科学习应该让这些孩子变得温文尔雅<br>'),(8884,'preparation','','','','preparations','n. 准备',' Preparations for the Queen\'s visit are almost complete.<br>     女王访问的筹备工作已基本就绪。<br>\n He didn\'t do any preparation for this exam, so he failed.<br>     他考试前没做任何准备，所以不及格。<br>'),(8885,'preparatory','','','','preparatories','a. 预备的,准备的,初步的',' They finished the preparatory training.<br>     他们完成了预备训练。<br>\n What are your preparatory measures?<br>     你的初步措施是什么？<br>'),(8886,'prepare','prepared','prepared','preparing','','v. 准备,预备',' He is preparing his speech for the meeting tomorrow.<br>     他正准备明天集会的演说。<br>\n Early experiments with military rockets prepared the ground for space travel.<br>     早年对军用火箭进行的实验为发展航天技术奠定了基础。<br>'),(8887,'prepared','','','','','a. 有准备的(特别处理过的)<br>\nv. 准备',' They prepared rice, flour and sundry other items of food for the poor.<br>     他们为穷人准备了米，面及其它各种食物。<br>\n I have prepared everything for the trip.<br>     我做好了旅行的所有准备。<br>'),(8888,'prepay','prepaid','prepaid','prepaying','','v. 预付',' The telegram was sent reply prepaid.<br>     电报已发出并已预付复电费用。<br>\n I use a prepaid envelope.<br>     我用了一个邮资已付的信封。<br>'),(8889,'preponderance','','','','','n. 优势,多数',''),(8