。<br>'),(9171,'pronounce','pronounced','pronounced','pronouncing','','v. 发音,宣告,断言',' I don\'t know how to pronounce this word.<br>     我不知道这个单词怎么发音。<br>\n The court pronounced against my claim to the land.<br>     法庭宣判不承认我对这片土地的权益。<br>'),(9172,'pronounced','','','','','a. 显著的,断然的,明白的<br>\nvbl. 发音,宣告,断言',' The two words are spelled differently, but pronounced the same.<br>     这两个字拼写不同, 但发音相同.<br>\n Pronounced with the tongue in a middle position, neither high nor low, as the a in around.<br>     中性音的发音时舌头位于中间位置的，即不高也不低，如：around中的a音<br>'),(9173,'pronouncement','','','','','n. 宣布,宣告,声明,判决',' There has been no official pronouncement yet on the state of the president\'s health.<br>     官方尚未就总统的健康状况发表公告.<br>'),(9174,'pronunciation','','','','pronunciations','n. 发音',' You should look up the right pronunciation of this word in the dictionary.<br>     你应该查字典找出这个单词的正确读音。<br>\n Your faults of pronunciation can be remedied.<br>     你的发音毛病是可以纠正的。<br>'),(9175,'proof','proofed','proofed','proofing','proofs','a. 防...的,耐...的<br>\nn. 校样,证据,证明<br>\nv. 检验,校对<br>\nvt. 检验',' A soldier\'s courage is put to the proof in battle.<br>     士兵的勇气在战斗中得到考验。<br>\n Have you got any proof that you own this bike?<br>     你有什么证据证明这辆自行车是你的？<br>'),(9176,'proofread','proofread','proofread','proofreading','','v. 校对',' It\'s a part of your duties to proofread.<br>     校对是你的份内之事。<br>\n I have proofread twenty pages.<br>     我已经校对完二十页了。<br>'),(9177,'proofreader','','','','','n. 校对员',' His mistake got by the editor but was caught by the proofreader.<br>     他的错误被编辑忽视了但被校对员发现了<br>'),(9178,'prop','','','','','n. 支柱,支持者,倚靠人<br>\nv. 支撑,维持',' It is not the government\'s policy to prop up declining industries.<br>     资助不景气的工业不是政府的政策。<br>\n The invalid lay propped on the pillows.<br>     那病弱者倚靠在枕头上。<br>'),(9179,'propaganda','','','','','n. 宣传',' The anti-British propaganda gave (ie caused) much offence.<br>     反英宣传触犯了众怒.<br>\n Art may be used as a vehicle for propaganda.<br>     艺术可用作宣传工具.<br>'),(9180,'propagandist','','','','','n. 传播者,宣传者',' One who attempts to persuade or convert others to a particular program, doctrine, or set of principles; a propagandist.<br>     倡导者试图劝说或改变他人的观念使其相信某一特定项目，道理或原则的人；鼓吹者<br>'),(9181,'propagate','propagated','propagated','propagating','','v. 繁殖,传播,传送',' Most plants propagate by seed.<br>     大多数植物靠种子繁殖。<br>\n They started a newspaper to propagate their ideas.<br>     他们办了一份报纸来宣传他们的主张。<br>'),(9182,'propagation','','','','','n. 增殖,繁殖,广传',' The sun sometimes spoils the propagation of radio waves.<br>     太阳有时会影响无线电波的传播。<br>\n The systematic propagation of a doctrine or cause or of information reflecting the views and interests of those people advocating such a doctrine or cause.<br>     宣传活动对一个学说、事业或信息的系统宣传，其反映倡导该学说或该事业的人的观点和利益<br>'),(9183,'propane','','','','','n. 丙烷',''),(9184,'propel','propelled','propelled','propelling','','v. 推进,驱使',' His addiction to drugs propelled him towards a life of crime.<br>     他吸毒成瘾使他走上了犯罪的道路。<br>\n We are propelled to go forward.<br>     我们被推着向前走。<br>'),(9185,'propellent','','','','','a. 推进的',''),(9186,'propeller','','','','propellers','n. 螺旋桨,推进器',' Can you free the propeller from the weeds?<br>     你能把螺旋桨上的草除掉吗?<br>\n The distance that a propeller would travel in an ideal medium during one complete revolution, measured parallel to the shaft of the propeller.<br>     推进器转一圈的距离飞机螺旋桨旋转一次的前移距离，以其与螺旋桨相平行的距离衡量<br>'),(9187,'propensity','','','','propensities','n. 倾向,习性',' A propensity for being displeased with anything that is not perfect or does not meet extremely high standards.<br>     完美主义对于任何不完美或未达到最高标准的事都有不满意的倾向<br>\n A disposition to feel, do, or say; a propensity.<br>     意向感觉、做或说的意向；倾向<br>'),(9188,'proper','','','','','a. 适当的,正确的,合适的,正当的,规矩的',' The pages aren\'t in proper order.<br>     这些页数次序不对。<br>\n His mother has trained him to be a very proper young man.<br>     他的母亲已经把他训练成循规蹈矩的人。<br>'),(9189,'properly','','','','','ad. 适当地,相当地,当然地',' I\'m learning German, but I still can\'t speak it properly.<br>     我正在学习德语，但还说不好。<br>\n That is not, properly speaking, a dictionary but a grammar book.<br>     严格地说，那不是一本字典，而是一本语法书。<br>'),(9190,'property','','','','properties','n. 财产,性质',' The police found some stolen property in the thief\'s house.<br>     警察在小偷的家里发现了一些被盗的财物。<br>\n Many plants have medicinal properties.<br>     许多植物具有医药性能。<br>'),(9191,'prophecy','','','','prophecies','n. 预言,预言能力',' His prophecy was fulfilled.<br>     他的预言应验了。<br>\n The god of prophecy, music, medicine, and poetry, sometimes identified with the sun.<br>     阿波罗司预言、音乐、医药、诗歌之神，有时等同于太阳神<br>'),(9192,'prophesy','prophesied','prophesied','prophesying','','v. 预言,预报',' He prophesied that war would break out.<br>     他预言说战争将要爆发。<br>\n He prophesied of strange things to come.<br>     他预言将有怪事发生。<br>'),(9193,'prophet','','','','prophets','n. 预言者,先知,提倡者',' The prophet said that war will break out.<br>     先知预言战争将爆发。<br>\n Daughter of the Islamic prophet Mohammed. She married Ali, among the first to embrace Islam, and is considered by Moslems to be one of the Four Perfect Women.<br>     法蒂玛伊斯兰先知穆罕默德的女儿。她嫁给了首批皈依伊斯兰教的阿里，被穆斯林认为是四个完美女人之一<br>'),(9194,'prophetic','','','','','a. 预言的,先知的,预示的',' His prophetic remarks frightened us.<br>     他那预言性的话吓着了我们。<br>\n Prophetic significance or meaning.<br>     预示预言性的意义或意思<br>'),(9195,'prophylactic','','','','','a. 预防疾病的',' A prophylactic agent, device, or measure, such as a vaccine or drug.<br>     预防剂预防性的物质、器具或措施，比如疫苗或药物<br>'),(9196,'propinquity','','','','','n. 邻近,亲近',' The neighbours lived in close propinquity toeach other.<br>     这些邻居住得很近.<br>'),(9197,'propitiate','propitiated','propitiated','propitiating','','v. 慰抚,安抚,和解',' They offered sacrifices to propitiate the gods.<br>     他们供奉祭品以求神息怒.<br>'),(9198,'propitiatory','','','','','a. 讨好的,调解的',''),(9199,'propitious','','','','','a. 顺利的,适合的,吉祥的',' It was not a propitious time to start a new business.<br>     这个时候开张不吉利。<br>\n The circumstances were not propitious for further expansion of the company.<br>     这些情况不利于公司的进一步发展。<br>'),(9200,'proponent','','','','','n. 建议者,支持者',' A closet proponent of a tax increase; a closet alcoholic.<br>     增加税收的私下倡议者；私下酗酒者<br>\n One who originates or is the chief proponent of a heresy or heretical movement.<br>     异端创始或领导人异端邪说或运动的发起者或主要倡导者<br>'),(9201,'proportion','proportioned','proportioned','proportioning','proportions','n. 比例,均衡,部份',' This painting lacks proportion.<br>     这幅画比例失调。<br>\n We are trying to reduce the problem to manageable proportions.<br>     我们正努力把问题缩小到可以控制的范围内。<br>'),(9202,'proportional','','','','proportionals','a. 成比例的,相称的<br>\nn. [数]比例项',' A pictorial representation of numerical data or relationships, especially a graph, but having each value represented by a proportional number of pictures.<br>     统计图表，象形图用图画表现数字的信息或关系，尤指图表，但用有比例的一定数字的图画来代表每种价值<br>\n Pertaining to a device that operates in a proportional or continuous manner, such as an analog amplifier. Not discrete or digital, but analog.<br>     用于修饰或说明一种设备（工作特性）的术语，这种设备以成比例或连续方式进行工作，例如用于说明模拟放大器的工作特性不是离散的或数字的，而是模拟的。<br>'),(9203,'proportional representation','','','','','n. (按得票的比例获得议员席位的)比例代表制',''),(9204,'proportionally','','','','','ad. 按比例(配合着,相应地,比较地)',''),(9205,'proportionately','','','','','ad. 相称地, 成比例地',''),(9206,'proposal','','','','proposals','n. 求婚,提议,建议',' Have you accepted his proposal?<br>     你答应他的求婚了吗？<br>\n Some members of the committee expressed reservations about the proposal.<br>     委员会一些成员对这项提议持保留态度。<br>'),(9207,'propose','proposed','proposed','proposing','','v. 计划,打算,向...提议',' Did he propose to you?<br>     他向你求婚了吗？<br>\n He proposed that a change should be made.<br>     他建议做一些改变。<br>'),(9208,'proposed','','','','','被提议的',' A plan that is proposed.<br>     提议被提议的一个计划<br>\n The Board of Education accounts for about a fourth of the city\'s budget. For1989, Mr.Koch proposed to spend$123 million on new and expanded programs, bringing the board\'s total budget to$6.3 billion.<br>     教育局约占全市预算的四分之一。葛德华先生提出将在1989年度花费1亿2300万元在新添及扩大的项目，使该局全部预算达到63亿元。<br>'),(9209,'proposition','propositioned','propositioned','propositioning','propositions','n. 建议,命题,主张<br>\nv. 向...提议,向...调情',' Tunnelling under the English Channel is a big proposition.<br>     在英吉利海峡海底凿隧道是一个大问题。<br>\n She was propositioned by her boss.<br>     她的老板向她提出非分的要求。<br>'),(9210,'propound','propounded','propounded','propounding','','v. 提出(问题)<br>\nvt. 提议',''),(9211,'proprietary','','','','proprietaries','a. 专利的(所有的)<br>\nn. 所有权(所有人)',' One granted ownership of a proprietary colony.<br>     领主独占某殖民地所有权的人<br>\n A proprietary hospital.<br>     一家私人医院<br>'),(9212,'proprietor','','','','proprietors','n. 所有者,经营者',' I\'ve written a complaint to the proprietor of the hotel.<br>     我向旅馆老板写信投诉。<br>\n The right of a proprietor to ownership of such addition or increase.<br>     财产自然增益权物主拥有这些增加价值的权力<br>'),(9213,'proprietorship','','','','','n. 所有权',''),(9214,'propriety','','','','proprieties','a. 适当<br>\nn. 礼节,适当',' The way these tourists dress offends local standards of propriety.<br>     这些游客的穿着在当地人的眼中简直不成体统。<br>\n We should observe the proprieties.<br>     我们应该遵守礼节。<br>'),(9215,'propulsion','','','','','n. 推进,推进力',' This aircraft works by jet propulsion.<br>     这架飞机是喷气推进的。<br>\n A part or surface, such as a wing, propeller blade, or rudder, whose shape and orientation control stability, direction, lift, thrust, or propulsion.<br>     翼剖面；机翼；翼面一个部件或平面，如机翼、螺旋桨叶、方向舵等，其形状或方位控制稳定性、方向、抬升、冲击或驱动<br>'),(9216,'propulsive','','','','','a. 推进的,有推进力的',''),(9217,'prorogue','prorogued','prorogued','proroguing','','v. 休会,延期',''),(9218,'prosaic','','','','','a. 单调的,无趣的',' A quality or style that is prosaic.<br>     平淡无奇平凡的特点或风格<br>\n The office seems so dull and prosaic after Pine Ridge.<br>     从松岭回来后，办公室似乎变得枯燥无味了。<br>'),(9219,'proscenium','','','','proscenia','n. 舞台前部(幕前部分)',''),(9220,'proscribe','proscribed','proscribed','proscribing','','vt. 不予法律保护(排斥)',' The sale of narcotics is proscribed by law.<br>     法律禁止贩卖毒品.<br>'),(9221,'proscription','','','','','n. 剥夺人权,处罚的宣告,放逐',''),(9222,