'),(10787,'rounding','','','','','舍入,凑整',' A rounding up and driving of cattle to new pastures or to market.<br>     驱赶牛群圈集并驱赶牛群到新的牧场或市场<br>\n The bill should have been$29.54 so I round it up to$30.<br>     账单本来应该是92。54美元，我凑个整数把它调高到了30美元。<br>'),(10788,'roundsman','','','','roundsmen','n. 稽查员,推销员',' Ask your roundsman for extra milk over Christmas.<br>     请贵店送货员在圣诞节多送些牛奶来.<br>'),(10789,'roundup','','','','','n. 集拢,围捕,综述,摘要',''),(10790,'rouse','roused','roused','rousing','','n. 觉醒,奋起<br>\nv. 唤醒,鼓舞,激动',' The dog roused a deer from the bushes.<br>     狗惊起了丛林中的一只鹿。<br>\n The news roused great indignation.<br>     这条消息引起了极大的愤慨。<br>'),(10791,'rout','','','','','n. 彻底溃败,凑热闹的人,大败<br>\nv. 使...溃败,使...败逃',' They routed the enemy.<br>     他们打败并赶走了敌人。<br>\n Our party was routed at the election.<br>     我们党在竞选中被彻底击败了。<br>'),(10792,'route','routed','routed','routing','routes','n. 航线,路线<br>\nvt. 按路线发送',' We drove home by a roundabout route.<br>     我们绕远道驾车回家。<br>\n The flight is routed to Chicago via New York.<br>     这个航班被安排经纽约飞往芝加哥。<br>'),(10793,'router','','','','','路由程序,路由器',''),(10794,'routine','','','','routines','a. 常规的,例行的<br>\nn. 例行公事,常规',' It was a rather routine performance.<br>     那是很一般的演出。<br>\n She found it difficult to establish a new routine after retirement.<br>     她发觉退休后很难建立起新的生活规律。<br>'),(10795,'routinely','','','','','ad. 通常',''),(10796,'routing','','','','','路由选择,路径选择',' A line or list formed by items in a system waiting for service; for example, tasks to be performed or messages to be transmitted in a message routing system.<br>     由系统中等待服务的项目构成的行或列表，例如等待执行的任务或在报文路由选择系统中等待发送的报文。<br>\n The routing or controlling routines of Subsystem Support Services. This routine provides multitasking and control support, on a priority basis, for all Subsystem Support Services functions.<br>     子系统支持服务程序的路径选择或控制程序。此程序根据所有子系统支持服务功能的优先级提供多任务和控制支持。<br>'),(10797,'rove','roved','roved','roving','','n. 徘徊,粗纺线,流浪<br>\nv. 漂泊于,漫游于,飘忽不定',' He rove about his student.<br>     他扫了他的学生一