的前途赌在航天飞机及太空站一类的硬件上。<br>\n During this exercise, the spaceship will be locked onto the other side of the space station, so that the men can move from one vehicle to the other.<br>     这次演习中，宇宙飞船将紧紧地靠上宇航站的另一边，这样宇航员就可以从一个飞行器走到另一个飞行器上了。<br>'),(12531,'spacecraft','','','','spacecraft','n. 宇宙飞船',' The spacecraft is orbiting the moon.<br>     宇宙飞船正绕月球飞行。<br>\n The scientists calculated when the spacecraft would reach the moon.<br>     科学家推算出宇宙飞船抵达月球的时间。<br>'),(12532,'spaceship','','','','spaceships','n. 宇宙飞船',' The spaceship traveled smoothly in the universe.<br>     太空船在宇宙里平稳地飞行。<br>\n There are five spacemen in the spaceship.<br>     宇宙飞船里有五个飞行员。<br>'),(12533,'spacing','','','','','n. 留间隔,空隙,排字法',' Spaces or a space, as in printed matter.<br>     字距空隙或空白，如印刷品中<br>\n In typewriters, spacing of10 characters to the inch.<br>     在打字机中，一英寸十个字符的间隔。<br>'),(12534,'spacious','','','','','a. 广阔的,宽敞的',' In its spacious halls are displayed over8000 priceless relics.<br>     在它宽敞的大厅里，展出了8000多件珍贵文物。<br>\n The systematic arrangement of chairs makes the hall look spacious.<br>     座椅按照顺序排列，这使得礼堂里显得很宽敞。<br>'),(12535,'spade','','','','','n. 铲子,铁锹<br>\nv. 铲<br>\nvt. (用铲子)铲',' Orders came that we should spade the trench in an hour.<br>     有命令要我们必须在一小时内挖好战壕。<br>\n We dig some pits with a spade before planting the trees.<br>     种树前，我们先用铁锹挖了些坑。<br>'),(12536,'spades','','','','','锹(复数)',' The soldiers cut a passage through the jungle with their spades.<br>     士兵们用铁锹在丛林中开出一条道路。<br>\n He told me the whole story in spades and there\'s no doubt about it.<br>     他明确地把整个经过都对我讲了，一点不含糊。<br>'),(12537,'spaghetti','','','','','n. 意大利式细面条',' Pasta made in long strands thinner than spaghetti.<br>     细面条，线面做成长条形，比意大利式细面条更细的意大利面食<br>\n Spaghetti is one of my favorite foods.<br>     义大利式细面条是我喜欢的食品之一。<br>'),(12538,'Spain','','','','','n. 西班牙',' I was told that Spain is a romantic nation.<br>     有人告诉我说，西班牙是个浪漫的国家。<br>\n Spain used to be famous for its strong armada.<br>     西班牙曾以其强大的舰队而著称.<br>'),(12539,'