use of the power.<br>     他因滥用职权而破坏了政治声誉。<br>'),(13790,'tainted','','','','','a. 感染的,污染的',' Throw that tainted meat away; it\'s not edible.<br>     把那块腐烂的肉扔掉，不能再吃了。<br>\r\n His political reputation was tainted by his abuse of the power.<br>     他因滥用职权而破坏了政治声誉。<br>'),(13791,'Taipei','','','','','n. 台北',' It rains a lot in Taipei.<br>     在台北下很多的雨。<br>\r\n The climate here is like that of Taipei.<br>     这儿的气候和台北非常相似。<br>'),(13792,'Taiwan','','','','','n. 台湾',' He is said to have been the richest man in Taiwan.<br>     据说他以前是台湾最有钱的人。<br>\r\n Taiwan is southeast of China.<br>     台湾在中国的东南。<br>'),(13793,'take','took','taken','taking','','v. (took,taken) 拿,取<br>\r\nv. 修(课程),花费,记录,认为,搭乘',' I passed him the rope and he took it.<br>     我递给他绳子，他接住了。<br>\r\n The machine takes its name from its inventor.<br>     这机器的名字来自其发明者。<br>'),(13794,'Take care','','','','','当心,注意',' You are not (physically) strong, so you may as well take care of your health.<br>     你的体格不壮，因此最好注意健康。<br> Take care (that) you don\'t drink too much/not to drink too much.<br>     当心别喝多了.<br>'),(13795,'Take your time','','','','','vt. 从容做(不慌不忙)',' It\'s an important decision for you, so take your time to think it over.<br>     对你来说，这是一个十分重要的决定，仔细考虑一下吧。<br> It is better to take your time at this job than to hurry and make mistakes.<br>     做这份工作还是慢慢来好些，不要匆忙弄出错误。<br>'),(13796,'takeaway','','','','','卖出外吃的<br>\r\n外卖饭菜的',''),(13797,'take-away','','','','','n.&a. (可带走的)熟食',' I\'m too tired to cook let\'s get something from the Chinese take-away.<br>     我累得做不了饭了--咱们从中国外卖餐馆买些东西来吃吧.<br>\r\n I fancy an Indian take-away.<br>     我想吃外卖的印度饭菜.<br>'),(13798,'taken','','','','','take的过去分词',' After being taken back 200 years, we were suddenly returned to the present day.<br>     我们刚才还处在200年前的历史场景之中, 一下子又回到了现在.<br>\r\n The criminal was taken into custody.<br>     这个罪犯已被监禁。<br>'),(13799,'takeout','','','','','a. 供顾客带出外吃的,外卖的食物',''),(13800,'takeover','','','','','n. 接收(验收)',' Before the hostile takeover, the purchaser often 