ty chatter really tested my patience.<br>     听他那没完没了的连篇空话对我的耐心真是一大考验。<br>'),(14095,'test paper','','','','','n. [化]试纸',' He is answering the test paper busily.<br>     他正忙着答考试卷。<br>\r\n He erased pencil marks form the test paper and handed to the teacher.<br>     他擦去试卷上的铅笔笔迹然后递给了老师。<br>'),(14096,'test tube','','','','','试管',' He held the test tube in his hand thoughtfully.<br>     他沉思地把试管拿在手里。<br>\r\n He demonstrated the principles with chemicals and test tubes.<br>     他借助化学药品和试管讲解了这些原理。<br>'),(14097,'testable','','','','','a. 可试验的',''),(14098,'testament','','','','testaments','n. 圣约,与神的誓约,圣约书',' Her solicitor drew up her last will and testament.<br>     她的律师拟就了她的遗嘱。<br>\r\n This aircraft\'s safety record is an impressive testament to its designers\' skill.<br>     这种飞机的飞行安全记录令人印象深刻，证明了该机种设计师本领非凡。<br>'),(14099,'testator','','','','','n. 立遗嘱之人',' One that makes a will; a testator.<br>     遗赠人，立遗嘱者设立遗嘱的人；立遗嘱者<br>\r\n A will needs the signature of the testator and two witness.<br>     一份遗嘱需要立遗嘱人和两个证人的签字。<br>'),(14100,'test-drive','','','test-driving','','v. 试开',''),(14101,'testify','testified','testified','testifying','','v. 证明,作证',' All kinds of human experience testify to the close link between love and fear.<br>     人类的种种经验都证明了爱与怕之间的紧密联系。<br>\r\n He agreed to testify on behalf of the accused man.<br>     他同意为被告作证。<br>'),(14102,'testimonial','','','','testimonials','n. 证明书,奖状',' She sent a testimonial from her former employer when applying for the post.<br>     她申请那职位时寄去了前雇主的推荐书.<br>\r\n The boy look for a job have testimonial from his teacher and former employer.<br>     那个找工作的小伙子有他的老师和以前的雇主的推荐信。<br>'),(14103,'testimony','','','','testimonies','n. 证言,证据',' Several men were called for testimony.<br>     好几个人被传来作证。<br>\r\n The witness is giving false testimony.<br>     那个证人在作伪证。<br>'),(14104,'testing','','','','','n. 测试<br>\r\na. 吃力的,试验的<br>\r\nvbl. 尝试,测验',' We are testing the efficacy of a new drug.<br>     我们正在测试新药的功效。<br>\r\n Imitation or representation, as of a potential situation or in experimental testing.<br>     模拟模仿或演习可能发生的情况或在试验性的测试中进行模仿和演习<br>'),(14105,'testosterone','','','','','n. 男性荷尔蒙的一种',''),(14106,'test-tube','','','','','n. 试管',''),(14107,'testy','','','','','a. 易怒的,暴躁的','');
INSERT INTO `words` VALUES (14108,'tetanus','','','','','n. 破伤风',' German physiologist. He won a1901 Nobel Prize for work on serum immunization against diphtheria and tetanus.<br>     贝林，埃米尔·冯1854－1917德国生理学家，因其在抗白喉与破伤风血清免疫方面的工作获1901年诺贝尔奖<br>'),(14109,'tether','tethered','tethered','tethering','tethers','n. 系绳,系链,界限<br>\r\nv. 练栓,拘束',' He tethered his horse to a tree.<br>     他用绳子把马拴在树上。<br>\r\n The animals were fastened by tether.<br>     那群牲畜被绳子拴着。<br>'),(14110,'tetrad','','','','','四位组',''),(14111,'tetrahedron','','','','tetrahedrons','n. 四面体',''),(14112,'tetrahydrocannabinol','','','','','n. [化]四氢大麻醇,四氢大麻酚(大麻树脂的主要成分,麻醉用)',''),(14113,'Texas','','','','','n. 德克萨斯州,(美国州名)',' As a rule of thumb, a one-cent-a-gallon gasoline tax raises$1 billion. Oil producers in President-elect Bush\'s adopted state of Texas, however, would rather see a tax on imported crude oil.<br>     一般情形是，每加仑加汽油一分钱的税可以征收10亿元。可是，在布什第二家乡德克萨斯州的产油商宁愿看见在进口原油上征税。<br>\r\n He is rated one of the rich men in Texas.<br>     他被认为是德州最富有的人之一。<br>'),(14114,'text','','','','texts','n. 本文,文件,正文<br>\r\nv. 发短信',' He studied Shakespeare\'s texts.<br>     他学习了莎士比亚的原作。<br>\r\n The book contains scandalous text.<br>     该书含有诽谤性的内容。<br>'),(14115,'textbook','','','','textbooks','n. 课本,教科书',' Our textbook is very well illustrated.<br>     我们的课本插图丰富。<br>\r\n This is the standard textbook on the subject.<br>     这是这一科的权威性课本.<br>'),(14116,'textile','','','','textiles','a. 纺织的<br>\r\nn. 纺织品',' Their main exports are textiles, especially silk and cotton.<br>     他们的主要出口货物是纺织品，特别是丝绸和棉布。<br>\r\n I got a job in a textile factory.<br>     我在一家纺织厂找到一份工作。<br>'),(14117,'textual','','','','','a. 本文的,原文的',' Textual analysis identified the author as Shakespeare.<br>     对原文的分析研究鉴定出作者是莎士比亚.<br>\r\n Mail permits network users to send textual messages to each other.<br>     电子邮件允许网络用户彼此传送文本消息。<br>'),(14118,'texture','','','','textures','n. (材料等的)结构,质地',' This kind of cloth has a close texture.<br>     这种布质地很紧密。<br>\r\n The cake has a nice