  这是谁的钢笔？<br>'),(15164,'why','','','','whys','ad. 为什么<br>\r\nconj. …的理由,为什么<br>\r\nint. 咳,哎呀<br>\r\npron. 为何,为什么',' Why not let her do as she likes?<br>     为什么不让她想怎么做就怎么做呢？<br>\r\n The reasons why he did it are obscure.<br>     他做那事的理由还不清楚。<br>'),(15165,'wicked','','','','','a. 坏的,邪恶的,缺德的',' The little boy had a wicked twinkle in his eyes.<br>     这个男孩的眼睛里闪烁着调皮的光。<br>\r\n It\'s a wicked waste of money.<br>     这样浪费金钱简直是罪恶。<br>'),(15166,'wide','','','','','a. 广泛的,宽阔的<br>\r\nad. 广大地,全部地',' She stared at him with wide eyes.<br>     她睁大眼睛注视他。<br>\r\n He is a man of wide interests.<br>     他兴趣广泛。<br>'),(15167,'widely','','','','','a. 广泛的<br>\r\nad. 广泛地',' This accident is widely known.<br>     这场事故众所周知。<br>\r\n They differ widely in their opinions.<br>     他们的意见分歧很大。<br>'),(15168,'widen','widened','widened','widening','','v. 弄宽',' He wants to widen his knowledge of the industry.<br>     他想扩充自己在这一行业的知识。<br>\r\n The road is being widened.<br>     这条路正在拓宽。<br>'),(15169,'widening','','','','','扩展,加宽',' A widening in a highway to allow vehicles to pass or park.<br>     避车道，停车道高速分路上可以错车或停的宽大空间<br>\r\n A gap between revenue and spending; the widening gap between rich and poor.<br>     收入和消费之间的差距；富人与穷人之间很大的悬殊<br>'),(15170,'widespread','','','','','a. 分布(或散布)广的,普遍的',' The forests are widespread in our country.<br>     我们的国家森林分布很广。<br>\r\n Widespread flooding is affecting large areas of Devon.<br>     洪水泛滥, 淹没了德文郡的广大地区.<br>'),(15171,'widow','widowed','widowed','widowing','widows','n. 寡妇',' That widow is a kind person.<br>     那个寡妇是个善良的人。<br>\r\n We had compassion for the poor widow.<br>     我们同情这个可怜的寡妇。<br>'),(15172,'widower','','','','widowers','n. 鳏夫',' The widower did not remarry.<br>     那鳏夫未曾再娶.<br>\r\n Once old Joe had inured himself to the solitary life of a widower, he began to improve in health and spirit.<br>     一旦老乔适应了鳏夫的孤独生活，他的身体和精神状况便开始好转了。<br>'),(15173,'width','','','','widths','n. 宽度',' The garden is six meters in width.<br>     花园的宽度为六米。<br>\r\n Tornadoes are vio